lxde-common (0.5.0-4) unstable; urgency=low

  [ Andrew Lee (李健秋) ]
  * debian/README.Debian:
    - Update README.Debian for 'startx' users. (Closes:#570083)
    - Document default hotkeys for default openbox-lxde WM
